{"tid":1585474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[講到斷氣] Twitter 文宣最有效呀! 唔識用教埋你用好未!","createTime":"2019-09-21T15:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T15:10:42.000Z","uid":173627,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbf88170be75e788184cacbe4b31e9dee2459a0","tid":1585474,"uid":173627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:23:16.000Z","msg":"講咗幾多次<br />\n點解Twitter 文宣最有效呀? <br />\n<br />\n因為調查記者全部都鐘意用Twitter 揾料呀!! 同普通網民文宣緊要，定同人地啲記者文宣緊要呀? 人地喺自己國家寫一句好過你喺Reddit推十個post<br />\n<br />\nReddit 連登個search 廢到一個點，Facebook Youtube 要本身識去邊個page 先睇到香港片。Twitter 只要夠多人一齊用同一個hashtag 出post，個hashtag 就自動上每日trending hashtag list，人人都會喺homepage 右手邊見到 #HongKongProtest<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgr9XVL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffgr9XVL.png&h=6153e74f&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以Twitter要人!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n再教你用記者偏愛Twitter嘅最大原因--Tweetdeck，輕鬆收風<br />\n1. 開Twitter 帳號 + 喺電腦登入<br />\n2.  去 <a href=\"https://tweetdeck.twitter.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftweetdeck.twitter.com%2F&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=30adb5b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tweetdeck.twitter.com/</a> ，會見到下面網頁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A490kcb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA490kcb.png&h=4c988f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTweetdeck每一列等於一個搜尋結果，最重要係每一列都會<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>自動更新</strong></span></span>。列1至列三都係搜尋關鍵字同hashtags，列寧就特別啲，係搜尋一組自訂嘅用戶嘅動態，要新增就要撳左手邊深藍色工具列個箭嘴，會出咗: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhkyFfw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhkyFfw.png&h=33693218&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n撳&quot;List&quot;，就會俾你㨂列寧要follow邊個用戶。<br />\n<br />\n所以連登仔們，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">乖啦! 用Twitter啦! </span></strong></span><br />\n真係求你地，唔洗淨用Twitter，但係起碼得閒去Twitter開個post幫手推hashtag <br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可!<br />\n光復香港，時代革命!"},{"pid":"c9743f5d8ff29e97fa6e406d3f8248abe8022704","tid":1585474,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:25:14.000Z","msg":"漏咗步，撳左手邊深藍色工具列個箭嘴之後再撳&quot;Add column&quot;"},{"pid":"775fec61326dc6531323f432eef0ac68f4854bfb","tid":1585474,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:25:43.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"5745108b89d85e307a2afe2473053dd211d5e8df","tid":1585474,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:26:16.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"f0ef7d08efca1ac96c2fb5afe618a6c60c25e72a","tid":1585474,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:27:23.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"f846d4ccb6413f4533b5f5d70bc399233b5a4eab","tid":1585474,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"2d0d36e68d78844223167ad08f4c40d0363b8904","tid":1585474,"uid":284463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"我愛香港 我要清潔18區連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585340</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6736b7df09fa1fe764e214b71c0ae3f253831379","tid":1585474,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:29:36.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"ad527aeafa6864f2fd315fb085b355b436efe701","tid":1585474,"uid":271234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:30:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"cc69c307adefff9e250cb3145e170c4cf774dc58","tid":1585474,"uid":46006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201